‚ú® Key Features
The Vital Bloom: A generative biofeedback interface that pulses with the user's real-time heart rate, turning data into a calming visual sanctuary.
The Village Constellation: A privacy-first resonance map. Users appear as stars in a constellation, glowing with colors that represent their current energy levels (Indigo for rest, Amber for focus, Rose-Gold for connection).
Pulse for Help: A low-friction way to signal the "Village" when your battery is low, triggering a wave of collective calm or a simple "I'm with you" notification.
